race.comment: WYNBURN BLIZZARD (1) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished third (30.83) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. One of the contenders. UNCONVICTED (8) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at Hobart over 461m behind Glenroy (26.62) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Should be in this for a long way. NITRO PLUME (3) missed the hat-trick last start when sixth and beaten 8 lengths (31.11) last time at this track. Warrants plenty of respect. OLLIE JACK (5) is worth some thought after placing in an impressive time last start.
